dct_title_s: New township and railroad map of the state of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Shows completed and unfinished railroad lines, the extent of surveyed townships, county boundaries, towns, and post offices in Minnesota.; Source of date of probable publication from an identical copy of map that has descriptive text on verso entitled "1882, Minnesota, the great agricultural, manufacturing and commercial state of the Northwest" describing these three characteristics as well as educational opportunities and unoccupied lands in Minnesota.; Inset: Minnesota's continental position.
dct_publisher_sm: Published by the State Board of Immigration (Saint Paul,  Minn.?)
